+ * ({@link org.commonmark.parser.Parser.Builder#extensions(Iterable)},
+ * {@link HtmlRenderer.Builder#extensions(Iterable)}).
+ * </p>
+ * <p>
+ * The parsed tables are turned into {@link TableBlock} blocks.
